OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781111161
OL,3,CTrump official: Somali referee had
OL,4,Clinks to 'suspected' terror group
OL,5,Cmembers
OL,7,FA Somali referee who was due to
OL,8,Fofficiate at the 2026 World Cup was
OL,9,Fdenied entry to the US because of
OL,10,Falleged links to "suspected members of
OL,11,Fterror organisations", a Trump
OL,12,Fadministration official has said.
OL,14,FOmar Artan, who was due to become the
OL,15,Ffirst Somali referee to officiate at a
OL,16,FWorld Cup match, was removed from the
OL,17,Flist of officials on Monday after he
OL,18,Fwas barred from entering the US at
OL,19,FMiami International Airport after
OL,20,Farriving from Istanbul on Saturday.
OL,26,@rD@ROUsD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781111161
OL,3,CTrump official: Somali referee had
OL,4,Clinks to 'suspected' terror group
OL,5,Cmembers
OL,7,FA Trump administration official told
OL,8,FITV News' US partner CNN on Wednesday
OL,9,Fthat Artan was denied entry following
OL,10,Fvetting checks that uncovered
OL,11,F"derogatory information, including
OL,12,Fassociation with suspected members of
OL,13,Fterror organisations".
OL,15,FThe official did not provide any
OL,16,Ffurther details about the alleged
OL,17,Flinks or the nature of the
OL,18,Fassociations.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
