OL,3,CTrump official: Somali referee had
OL,4,Clinks to 'suspected' terror group
OL,5,Cmembers
OL,7,FArtan returned to a hero's welcome at
OL,8,Fthe airport in Mogadishu on Wednesday,
OL,9,Fwhere he thanked the Somali
OL,10,Fgovernment, the Somali people and Fifa
OL,11,Ffor their support.
OL,13,FArtan, who was named the Confederation
OL,14,Fof African Football's referee of the
OL,15,Fyear in 2025, told hundreds of
OL,16,Fsupporters at the airport who waved
OL,17,Fthe Somali flag: "I promise you, God
OL,18,Fwilling, that I will attend the next
OL,19,Fone."
OL,26,@yD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
