OL,3,CTrump official: Somali referee had
OL,4,Clinks to 'suspected' terror group
OL,5,Cmembers
OL,7,F"I want the Somali public to take
OL,8,Fcomfort in this and remain confident."
OL,10,FArtan told The New York Times on
OL,11,FTuesday that he was "very
OL,12,Fdisappointed" with the decision and
OL,13,Fassured that he had the "right papers"
OL,14,Fto enter the country.
OL,16,F"I'm just simply a referee who's
OL,17,Ftrying to live his dream, the biggest
OL,18,Fdream of my life, to come to the World
OL,19,FCup," he said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@fO]xD@AOU{D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
