CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781111161
OL,3,CTrump official: Somali referee had
OL,4,Clinks to 'suspected' terror group
OL,5,Cmembers
OL,7,FArtan added: "I had the right papers
OL,8,Fand everything. I had the right visa."
OL,10,FWhen questioned by US border
OL,11,Fofficials, Artan said they reviewed
OL,12,Fonline information about his career.
OL,14,FAfter an 11-hour interview, he said he
OL,15,Fwas taken to a holding cell, where he
OL,16,Fwas detained for several more hours
OL,17,Fbefore being placed on a flight back
OL,18,Fto Istanbul.
OL,26,@oD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781111161
OL,3,CTrump official: Somali referee had
OL,4,Clinks to 'suspected' terror group
OL,5,Cmembers
OL,7,FArtan added that officials asked him
OL,8,Fwhy he had travelled to the US and
OL,9,Fquestioned him about politics in
OL,10,FSomalia.
OL,12,FAccording to Artan, many of the
OL,13,Fquestions focused on Al Shabab, the
OL,14,Fmilitant group that controls parts of
OL,15,FSomalia and has waged a long-running
OL,16,Finsurgency against the country's
OL,17,Fgovernment.
OL,19,FUS officials did not give him a reason
OL,20,Ffor refusing him entry to the country,
OL,21,FArtan said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
