OL,3,CTrump official: Somali referee had
OL,4,Clinks to 'suspected' terror group
OL,5,Cmembers
OL,7,FFifa, in a statement on Monday, said
OL,8,Fit was not involved in the immigration
OL,9,Fprocesses and was informed by
OL,10,Fauthorities that Artan's status "will
OL,11,Fnot be changed at present".
OL,13,F"In line with previous FIFA events, a
OL,14,Fhost government ultimately determines
OL,15,Fwho receives a visa and who is
OL,16,Fadmitted into their country," the
OL,17,Ffootball association said.
OL,19,FTrump suspended the entry of Somali
OL,20,Fnationals in June 2025, describing the
OL,21,Fcountry as a "terrorist safe haven".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
