OL,3,CTrump official: Somali referee had
OL,4,Clinks to 'suspected' terror group
OL,5,Cmembers
OL,7,FIt followed a January executive order,
OL,8,Fwhich called on the administration to
OL,9,Freport which countries had "deficient"
OL,10,Fvetting and screening information amid
OL,11,Fa crackdown on immigration.
OL,13,FThe entry of people from Afghanistan,
OL,14,FBurma, Chad, the Republic of the
OL,15,FCongo, Equatorial Guinea, Eritrea,
OL,16,FHaiti, Iran, Libya, Sudan, and Yemen
OL,17,Fis also suspended.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
