OL,3,CTrump official: Somali referee had
OL,4,Clinks to 'suspected' terror group
OL,5,Cmembers
OL,7,FIn its statement on Tuesday, the US
OL,8,FCustoms and Border Protection said all
OL,9,Ftravellers entering the US are subject
OL,10,Fto a vetting process.
OL,12,F"During processing, the traveller
OL,13,Funderwent additional inspection, a
OL,14,Froutine part of CBP's inspection
OL,15,Fprocess when officers need to verify
OL,16,Finformation or determine
OL,17,Fadmissibility," it said.
OL,26,@yD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
