FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781111161
OL,3,CTrump official: Somali referee had
OL,4,Clinks to 'suspected' terror group
OL,5,Cmembers
OL,7,F"Following inspection, the traveller,
OL,8,Fa referee for the FIFA World Cup, was
OL,9,Fdetermined to be inadmissible due to
OL,10,Fvetting concerns and was denied entry.
OL,12,F"Admissibility determinations are made
OL,13,Fon a case-by-case basis using law
OL,14,Fenforcement, national security, and
OL,15,Fimmigration information available at
OL,16,Fthe time of inspection," the statement
OL,17,Fcontinued.
OL,26,@xD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
