OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781111161
OL,3,CTrump official: Somali referee had
OL,4,Clinks to 'suspected' terror group
OL,5,Cmembers
OL,7,F"CBP officers have the authority to
OL,8,Fquestion travellers, conduct
OL,9,Finspections, and determine
OL,10,Fadmissibility consistent with US law."
OL,12,FFormer England striker Ian Wright
OL,13,Fcriticised the US' decision, ITV News
OL,14,FSports Editor Steve Scott reports
OL,16,FBritish football commentator and
OL,17,Fformer Arsenal player Ian Wright
OL,18,Fcriticised the decision to deny Artan
OL,19,Fentry in a video posted on his TikTok
OL,20,Fon Tuesday, calling the tournament a
OL,21,F"World Cup of chaos".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31012
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781111161
OL,3,CTrump official: Somali referee had
OL,4,Clinks to 'suspected' terror group
OL,5,Cmembers
OL,7,F"Every few hours, there's another
OL,8,Fstory about fans denied, players
OL,9,Fdenied, officials denied, journalists
OL,10,Fdenied, now refs? I'm laughing, but
OL,11,Fit's not funny, something has to be
OL,12,Fsaid," Wright said.
OL,14,F"It's the most expensive ticket ever.
OL,15,FExpensive accommodation, transport
OL,16,Fthrough the roof. It has to be said.
OL,17,FIs this how the hosts behave really,
OL,18,Ffor the greatest game, the greatest
OL,19,Ftournament in the world?"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31013
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781111161
OL,3,CTrump official: Somali referee had
OL,4,Clinks to 'suspected' terror group
OL,5,Cmembers
OL,7,F"How are we not hearing more? Is this
OL,8,Fthe spirit of football, really? You
OL,9,Fknow who I feel for, the American fans
OL,10,Fwho are desperate for this, how
OL,11,Fembarrassed they must be.
OL,13,F"This is a World Cup of chaos. Whoever
OL,14,Fwins this World Cup is going to have
OL,15,Fto go through some serious, serious
OL,16,Fchaos to get this done."
